<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="he" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SLH Spark Wallet — Send, Receive & Manage</title>
    <meta name="description" content="SLH Wallet - Multi-currency wallet with TON & BSC support. Send, receive, and manage your SLH, TON, and BNB tokens.">
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://slh-nft.com/wallet.html">
    <!-- Open Graph -->
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://slh-nft.com/wallet.html">
    <meta property="og:title" content="SLH Wallet - TON + BSC + CEX Portfolio">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Multi-currency wallet with QR codes, Bybit/Binance integration">
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://slh-nft.com/assets/og/wallet.png">
    <meta property="og:image:width" content="1200">
    <meta property="og:image:height" content="630">
    <meta property="og:locale" content="he_IL">
    <!-- Twitter Card -->
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="SLH Wallet - TON + BSC + CEX Portfolio">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="Multi-currency wallet with QR codes, Bybit/Binance integration">
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://slh-nft.com/assets/og/wallet.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32.png">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#050510">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/shared.css?v=20260421a">
    <style>
        .wallet-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: calc(var(--topnav-h) + 24px) 24px 100px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .wallet-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        .wallet-header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }
        .wallet-header i {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        /* ── Balance Cards ── */
        .balance-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
            gap: 16px;
        }
        .balance-card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 8px;
            transition: all var(--transition);
        }
        .balance-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent);
        }
        .balance-token {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text3);
        }
        .balance-token .token-icon {
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .token-slh { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2)); }
        .token-ton { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), #0088cc); }
        .token-bnb { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F0B90B, #F8D12F); }
        .token-locked { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--red), #cc3344); }

        .balance-amount {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.1;
        }
        .balance-fiat {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text3);
        }

        /* ── Send/Receive Tabs ── */
        .action-card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .action-tabs {
            display: flex;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .action-tab {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 14px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text3);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all var(--transition);
            border: none;
            background: none;
        }
        .action-tab:hover {
            color: var(--text);
        }
        .action-tab.active {
            color: var(--accent);
            background: var(--bg3);
            box-shadow: inset 0 -2px 0 var(--accent);
        }
        .action-body {
            padding: 24px;
        }
        .action-panel {
            display: none;
        }
        .action-panel.active {
            display: block;
        }

        /* Send Form */
        .send-form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 16px;
        }
        .send-form .form-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        .send-form .form-row .form-group {
            flex: 1;
        }
        .send-btn {
            padding: 14px;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all var(--transition);
            width: 100%;
        }
        .send-btn:hover {
            background: var(--accent2);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        /* Receive */
        .receive-panel {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .address-block {
            background: var(--bg3);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            padding: 16px;
        }
        .address-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: .05em;
            color: var(--text3);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .address-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        .address-value {
            flex: 1;
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--accent2);
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .address-copy-btn {
            padding: 6px 14px;
            background: var(--surface2);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-xs);
            color: var(--text2);
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all var(--transition);
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
        .address-copy-btn:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent);
            color: var(--accent);
        }
        .qr-placeholder {
            width: 160px;
            height: 160px;
            background: var(--bg3);
            border: 2px dashed var(--border2);
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--text3);
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* ── Transaction History ── */
        .history-card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .history-header {
            padding: 20px 24px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .history-header h2 {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .tx-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        .tx-table th {
            padding: 10px 16px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: .05em;
            color: var(--text3);
            background: var(--bg2);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        [dir="rtl"] .tx-table th {
            text-align: right;
        }
        .tx-table td {
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .tx-table tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .tx-table tr:hover td {
            background: var(--surface);
        }
        .tx-type-in { color: var(--green); }
        .tx-type-out { color: var(--red); }

        /* ── Token Info ── */
        .token-info-card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            padding: 24px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .token-info-card .token-badge {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #fff;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .token-info-details {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 200px;
        }
        .token-info-details .token-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .token-info-details .token-price-tag {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--gold);
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }
        .token-info-details .token-contract {
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text3);
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .token-info-details .token-contract a {
            color: var(--accent2);
        }

        /* ── Loading / Status ── */
        .loading-spinner {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            border: 2px solid var(--border);
            border-top-color: var(--accent);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: spin 0.8s linear infinite;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

        .api-status {
            font-size: 12px;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-xs);
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        .api-status.online { color: var(--green); }
        .api-status.offline { color: var(--red); }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .wallet-container { padding: calc(var(--topnav-h) + 16px) 16px 100px; }
            .balance-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
            .send-form .form-row { flex-direction: column; }
            .token-info-card { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
        }
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .balance-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }

        /* === WEB3 WALLET PANEL === */
        .web3-panel{
            background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--bg2,#111),var(--bg3,#1a1a1a));
            border:1px solid var(--border,rgba(255,255,255,.08));
            border-radius:12px;padding:24px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
        }
        .web3-panel::before{
            content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;
            background:linear-gradient(90deg,#f6851b,#e2761b,#00b4d8,#0077b6);
        }
        .web3-panel h3{
            font-size:15px;margin:0 0 6px 0;color:var(--text-bright,#fff);
            display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
        }
        .web3-panel h3 .web3-badge{
            font-size:9px;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:10px;
            background:rgba(246,133,27,.15);color:#f6851b;
            text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;font-weight:700;
        }
        .web3-panel .web3-sub{font-size:12px;color:var(--text2,#888);margin-bottom:16px}
        .btn-web3-connect{
            background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f6851b,#e2761b);
            color:#fff;border:none;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:10px;
            font-size:14px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;
            display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
            transition:.2s;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(246,133,27,.25);
        }
        .btn-web3-connect:hover{transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(246,133,27,.4)}
        .web3-addr{
            background:var(--card,rgba(255,255,255,.03));
            border:1px solid var(--border,rgba(255,255,255,.08));border-radius:8px;
            padding:10px 14px;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;
            color:var(--cyan,#00e5ff);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
            margin-bottom:16px;
        }
        .web3-balance-grid{
            display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(140px,1fr));
            gap:12px;margin-bottom:16px;
        }
        .web3-card{
            background:var(--card,rgba(255,255,255,.03));
            border:1px solid var(--border,rgba(255,255,255,.08));border-radius:10px;
            padding:14px;position:relative;transition:.2s;
        }
        .web3-card:hover{border-color:var(--accent,#00ff41);transform:translateY(-1px)}
        .web3-card .label{
            font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.2px;
            color:var(--text2,#888);display:block;margin-bottom:6px;
        }
        .web3-card .amount{
            font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-bright,#fff);
            font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;
        }
        .web3-card[data-token="SLH"]{border-left:3px solid #ffd700}
        .web3-card[data-token="BNB"]{border-left:3px solid #f3ba2f}
        .web3-card[data-token="ETH"]{border-left:3px solid #627eea}
        .web3-card[data-token="USDT"]{border-left:3px solid #26a17b}
        .btn-web3-disconnect{
            background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--border,rgba(255,255,255,.08));
            color:var(--text2,#888);padding:6px 14px;border-radius:8px;
            font-size:11px;cursor:pointer;transition:.2s;
        }
        .btn-web3-disconnect:hover{border-color:#ff0055;color:#ff0055}
        .web3-hint{
            margin-top:12px;padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(0,229,255,.05);
            border:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,.15);border-radius:8px;
            font-size:11px;color:var(--text2,#888);line-height:1.5;
        }
        @media(max-width:600px){
            .web3-panel{padding:18px}
            .web3-balance-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
        }
    </style>
    <!-- Web3 / ethers.js v6 for MetaMask + Trust Wallet -->
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/ethers/6.13.2/ethers.umd.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Top Nav -->
    <div id="topnav-root"></div>

    <!-- Ticker -->
    <div id="ticker-root"></div>

    <!-- Wallet Content -->
    <div class="wallet-container">

        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="wallet-header rv">
            <i class="fas fa-wallet"></i>
            <h1 data-i18n="wallet_title">Wallet</h1>
            <span id="api-status" class="api-status"></span>
        </div>

        <!-- Web3 Wallet Connection -->
        <div class="web3-panel rv" id="wallet-connect-section">
            <h3>
                <i class="fas fa-link"></i>
                <span data-i18n="web3_title">יתרות אמיתיות מהבלוקצ'יין</span>
                <span class="web3-badge">LIVE</span>
            </h3>
            <div class="web3-sub" data-i18n="web3_sub">חבר MetaMask, Trust Wallet או ארנק תואם WalletConnect כדי לראות את היתרות האמיתיות שלך ישירות מהרשת (BSC + ETH)</div>

            <div id="web3-status">
                <button id="btn-connect-wallet" class="btn-web3-connect">
                    <i class="fas fa-wallet"></i> <span data-i18n="web3_connect">חבר ארנק</span>
                </button>
                <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:10px">
                    <span style="padding:5px 10px;background:rgba(246,133,27,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(246,133,27,0.3);border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;color:#f6851b;font-weight:700">🦊 MetaMask</span>
                    <span style="padding:5px 10px;background:rgba(51,117,224,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(51,117,224,0.3);border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;color:#3375e0;font-weight:700">🛡 Trust Wallet</span>
                    <span style="padding:5px 10px;background:rgba(54,174,248,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(54,174,248,0.3);border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;color:#36aef8;font-weight:700">🔵 TonConnect</span>
                    <span style="padding:5px 10px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);font-weight:700">⚙ WalletConnect</span>
                </div>
                <div class="web3-hint" data-i18n="web3_hint" style="margin-top:12px">
                    במובייל: פתח את Trust Wallet → DApp Browser → הכנס <code>slh-nft.com/wallet.html</code><br>
                    <strong>האבטחה שלך מוגנת</strong> — אנחנו רק קוראים יתרות, לא שולחים עסקאות ולא מבקשים מפתחות.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="web3-balances" style="display:none">
                <div class="web3-addr">
                    <i class="fas fa-link"></i>
                    <span id="web3-addr-short">—</span>
                </div>
                <div class="web3-balance-grid">
                    <div class="web3-card" data-token="SLH">
                        <span class="label">SLH (BSC) 🔗</span>
                        <span class="amount" id="w3-slh">—</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="web3-card" data-token="BNB">
                        <span class="label">BNB 🔗</span>
                        <span class="amount" id="w3-bnb">—</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="web3-card" data-token="ETH">
                        <span class="label">ETH 🔗</span>
                        <span class="amount" id="w3-eth">—</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="web3-card" data-token="USDT">
                        <span class="label">USDT (BSC) 🔗</span>
                        <span class="amount" id="w3-usdt">—</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:10px">
                    <button id="btn-web3-refresh" class="btn-web3-connect" style="padding:6px 14px;font-size:12px" onclick="if(window.__slh_web3_last&&window.__slh_web3_last.address){renderWeb3Balances(window.__slh_web3_last.address);document.getElementById('web3-last-updated').textContent='רענון: '+new Date().toLocaleTimeString('he-IL')}">
                        🔄 רענן יתרות
                    </button>
                    <a id="web3-bscscan-link" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="font-size:12px;color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none;padding:6px 14px;border:1px solid var(--accent);border-radius:6px">
                        🔍 הצג ארנק ב-BSCScan
                    </a>
                    <span id="web3-last-updated" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);margin-right:auto"></span>
                </div>
                <button id="btn-disconnect-wallet" class="btn-web3-disconnect" data-i18n="web3_disconnect" style="margin-top:8px">
                    ✕ נתק ארנק
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Balance Cards -->
        <div class="balance-grid rv">
            <div class="balance-card">
                <div class="balance-token">
                    <span class="token-icon token-slh">S</span>
                    <span>SLH</span>
                </div>
                <div class="balance-amount" id="bal-slh">--</div>
                <div class="balance-fiat" id="bal-slh-fiat" data-i18n="wallet_available">Available</div>
            </div>
            <div class="balance-card">
                <div class="balance-token">
                    <span class="token-icon token-zvk" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#a855f7,#ec4899);color:#fff">Z</span>
                    <span>ZVK</span>
                </div>
                <div class="balance-amount" id="bal-zvk">--</div>
                <div class="balance-fiat" id="bal-zvk-fiat" data-i18n="zvk_balance">יתרת ZVK</div>
            </div>
            <div class="balance-card">
                <div class="balance-token">
                    <span class="token-icon token-ton"><i class="fas fa-gem" style="font-size:12px"></i></span>
                    <span>TON</span>
                </div>
                <div class="balance-amount" id="bal-ton">--</div>
                <div class="balance-fiat" id="bal-ton-fiat" data-i18n="wallet_available">Available</div>
            </div>
            <div class="balance-card">
                <div class="balance-token">
                    <span class="token-icon token-bnb"><i class="fas fa-coins" style="font-size:12px"></i></span>
                    <span>BNB</span>
                </div>
                <div class="balance-amount" id="bal-bnb">--</div>
                <div class="balance-fiat" id="bal-bnb-fiat" data-i18n="wallet_available">Available</div>
            </div>
            <div class="balance-card">
                <div class="balance-token">
                    <span class="token-icon token-locked"><i class="fas fa-lock" style="font-size:12px"></i></span>
                    <span>TON <small data-i18n="wallet_locked">Locked</small></span>
                </div>
                <div class="balance-amount" id="bal-ton-locked">--</div>
                <div class="balance-fiat" id="bal-ton-locked-fiat" data-i18n="wallet_locked">Locked</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ============================================================ -->
        <!-- EXTERNAL WALLETS — Bybit / Binance / Bitget / OKX / Self     -->
        <!-- ============================================================ -->
        <div class="web3-panel rv" style="margin-top:24px">
            <h3>
                <i class="fas fa-network-wired"></i>
                <span>הארנקים החיצוניים שלי</span>
                <span class="web3-badge" style="background:#00bcd4">READ-ONLY</span>
            </h3>
            <div class="web3-sub">
                הוסף כתובות ארנק מ-Bybit, Binance, Bitget, OKX או ארנק עצמי — נציג את היתרות שלך במקום אחד.
                <br><strong style="color:#22c55e">🔒 קריאה בלבד.</strong> אנחנו לא מבקשים מפתחות, חתימות או API keys.
